{"tid":1492610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯勸市民勿以暴制暴","createTime":"2019-08-21T02:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T02:35:08.000Z","uid":307145,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dccbd848afd29c215dfbb77ede63a0ddf229911f","tid":1492610,"uid":307145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2019/0821/20190821042320124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2019%2F0821%2F20190821042320124.jpg&h=2abc6e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  圖：民建聯、工聯會、新民黨的一眾議員、幹事及街坊到將軍澳警署請願，希望警方嚴正執法<br />\n<br />\n  【大公報訊】將軍澳昨日凌晨發生斬人案，震驚各界。新社聯昨發聲明強烈要求警方動用一切力量，盡快破案，懲治元兇。昨日上午，民建聯、工聯會、新民黨的一眾議員、幹事及街坊到將軍澳警署請願，希望警方嚴正執法，盡快緝拿斬人疑兇。<br />\n<br />\n  新社聯促依法嚴懲暴力<br />\n<br />\n  新社聯認為，社會須立即停止一切非法暴力，保障每一位市民安全。不管是何人所為，都要依法嚴懲，強烈要求特區政府再加大力度，採取更多有效措施應對各種的危機和挑戰，保障香港市民的生命財產安全和經濟民生。新社聯呼籲全港市民、社會各界齊心制止任何非法暴力，與非法暴力行為「割席」。不要讓香港社會再撕裂下去，應盡快重回安全和秩序。<br />\n<br />\n  民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆在直播中指出，香港近期發生很多暴力事件，但是絕對不要「以暴制暴」，認為暴力不能解決問題，又呼籲大家「放低暴力、放低仇恨」。葛珮帆又說，任何暴力事件絕對不能容忍、不能接受，要求警方嚴正執法，加強巡邏保障街坊的安全，又祝願傷者早日康復。"},{"pid":"9257e6fa688f14d09170fa096ca838ca43bd35eb","tid":1492610,"uid":32588,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"721 呢？<br />\n唔好意思，係佢地自己人做的，所以不會追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf2ceccc419e60864e4872d527c5259da5e29ee","tid":1492610,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"工聯會以暴制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f25af6485e4012d2b086bdcbcb0e767ffa9f59","tid":1492610,"uid":259812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:10:17.000Z","msg":"工聯會譴責暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84780c3f886477a1a5bb29d7b3e8afea6974a9c","tid":1492610,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"民建聯正垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491552/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491552/page/1</a><br />\n［ 8 2 4 和 你 suck ］行 動 更 新<br />\n建議大家不再分和理非勇武，合力&quot;搞&quot;好香港經濟先可以嬴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMbmerh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMbmerh.jpg&h=ba74c090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70e309b8d77470ae74a405853924117d6f9d1b0f","tid":1492610,"uid":75998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"佢地啲狗管唔著了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c02e94b7b32d30db729dfc48e6644532f08484a","tid":1492610,"uid":212973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:12:14.000Z","msg":"你同藍絲講啦"},{"pid":"11c7c8f0f7f0cbbaa34982c3b5efedceb91caffd","tid":1492610,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"用菠蘿就唔暴力了"},{"pid":"66ccb5308cd2ef28a6498c6ac6acc01ce5aa14a0","tid":1492610,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edf2ceccc419e60864e4872d527c5259da5e29ee","tid":1492610,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"工聯會以暴制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />工聯會係鼓吹主動出擊"},{"pid":"85319a74801f796f58c35ca96cde6c7f712ccecb","tid":1492610,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"唔要求係咪代表差佬唔會做野?<br />\n<br />\n差佬做份內事都要要求??"}]}